The '''Melody Fellowship''' was a group of [[Musician/Legends|musicians]] and agents that formed in response to the increased danger [[Artist/Legends|artists]] traveling [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] encountered during such times as the [[Stark Hyperspace War/Legends|Stark Hyperspace War]], [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], and other major conflicts.<ref name="HNN">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|56|business/13516_4.html|Balmorran Secures Musician Rearmament Contract}}</ref> The group was believed to have ordered production of the [[RO-D-series droid]] from [[Balmorran Arms/Legends|Balmorran Arms]].<ref name="SGTD">''[[Scavenger's Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

